data.title: Celebrity Jeopardy! Season 2
data.meta_description: Hollywood’s finest in television, film, comedy and more put their brainpower to the ultimate test in support of raising funds for charity.

Mo Rocca raised $250,000 for the Inner-City Scholarship Fund
